{"body": "Consider this features file:\r\n\r\n```gherkin\r\nFeature: Foo\r\n    Bar\r\n    Baz\r\n\r\n    Scenario: 123456789\r\n        Given some step\r\n\r\n    Scenario: 123456789 123456789 123456789\r\n```\r\n\r\nUpon executing lettuce -s 1, the longer scenario name will make the lettuce output unpleasantly long, despite no need for the extra space:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ lettuce -s 1\r\n\r\nFeature: Foo                              # features/subscribe_customer.feature:1\r\n  Bar                                     # features/subscribe_customer.feature:2\r\n  Baz                                     # features/subscribe_customer.feature:3\r\n\r\n  Scenario: 123456789                     # features/subscribe_customer.feature:5\r\n\r\n1 feature (1 passed)\r\n1 scenario (1 passed)\r\n0 step (0 passed)\r\n(finished within 1 seconds)\r\n```\r\n\r\nMy expectation is the output would look like this, as if the feature had been removed from the features file:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ lettuce\r\n\r\nFeature: Foo          # features/subscribe_customer.feature:1\r\n  Bar                 # features/subscribe_customer.feature:2\r\n  Baz                 # features/subscribe_customer.feature:3\r\n\r\n  Scenario: 123456789 # features/subscribe_customer.feature:5\r\n```\r\n", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/236/events", "updated_at": "2012-03-12T15:54:29Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/236/labels{/name}", "labels": [{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/labels/low-priority", "color": "d7e102", "name": "low-priority"}], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/236/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/236", "number": 236, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/JoshuaRodd/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/JoshuaRodd/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": 