{"body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n```gherkin\r\nScenario: Mark feature as successful\r\n  Given I defined a Background\r\n  And I defined a Scenario \r\n  When I run the Feature\r\n  And one/more Background steps fails\r\n  But no step from the Scenario fails\r\n  Then the Feature is marked as successful\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Deliverables\r\n\r\n```gherkin\r\nScenario: Mark feature as failed\r\n  Given I defined a Feature Background\r\n  And I defined a Feature Scenario \r\n  When I run the Feature\r\n  And one/more Background steps fails\r\n  But no step from the Scenario fails\r\n  Then the Feature is marked as failed\r\n\r\nScenario: Mark feature as successful\r\n  Given I defined a Feature Background\r\n  And I defined a Feature Scenario \r\n  When I run the Feature\r\n  And none of the Background steps fails\r\n  But none of the Scenario steps fails\r\n  Then the Feature is marked as successful\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\n#### Prerequisites\r\n ?\r\n\r\n#### TODO\r\n- ?\r\n\r\n#### Files\r\n- lettuce/core.py\r\n- lettuce/strings.py\r\n", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/427/events", "updated_at": "2014-02-03T12:25:48Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/427/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/427/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/427", "number": 427, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/marianitadn", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/ava