{"body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nIt seems that the Django hooks (before.each_app in particular) remains uncalled.\r\n\r\nI've debugged lettuce and found that in `harvest.py`:\r\n```python\r\nregistry.call_hook('before', 'harvest', locals())\r\nresults = []\r\ntry:\r\n    for path in paths:\r\n        app_module = None\r\n        if isinstance(path, tuple) and len(path) is 2:\r\n            path, app_module = path\r\n\r\n    if app_module is not None:\r\n        # THIS HOOK IS CALLED BEFORE INCLUDING ANY TEST FILE, SO THE FIRST TIME IT'S ALWAYS UNCALLED\r\n        registry.call_hook('before_each', 'app', app_module)\r\n\r\n    runner = Runner(path, options.get('scenarios'), verbosity,\r\n                    enable_xunit=options.get('enable_xunit'),\r\n                    xunit_filename=options.get('xunit_file'),\r\n                    tags=tags, failfast=failfast, auto_pdb=auto_pdb)\r\n\r\n    result = runner.run() # INSIDE THE run() ALL THE TEST FILES ARE INCLUDED\r\n    if app_module is not None:\r\n        registry.call_hook('after_each', 'app', app_module, result)\r\n```\r\nSo basically the hook is always called **before** including the decorated methods for the first time.\r\nI'll see if I have some time to propose a pull request but I think that this is something pretty urgent :\\\r\n\r\nThe needing of a `before.each_app` hook for me is essential because I have different kind of browsers instantiated for different apps, and no apps reference in the `before.each_scenario` or `before.each_feature`\r\n\r\nThis small hack can resolve the problem:\r\n```python\r\n    for path in paths:\r\n        app_module = None\r\n        if isinstance(path, tuple) and len(path) is 2:\r\n            path, app_module = path\r\n\r\n    if app_module is not None:\r\n        from lettuce.terrain import before\r\n        @before.all # THIS HOOK IS CALLED THE FIRST TIME IN THE run() METHOD\r\n        def call_before_each():\r\n            registry.call_hook('before_each', 'app', app_module)\r\n        call_before_each()\r\n```", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/331/events", "updated_at": "2013-03-04T11:53:19Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/331/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/331/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/331", "number": 331, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/vshjxyz", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/89b5a21e4070b8dd2f72f375776029e2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fca80d48dd093016f8b0aa38c0e40c07f.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/received_events", "gravatar_id": "89b5a21e4070b8dd2f72f375776029e2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "vshjxyz", "type": "User", "id": 958803, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/vshjxyz/followers"}, "milestone": null, "closed_at": null, "pull_request": {"diff_url": null, "html_url": null, "patch_url": null}, "id": 11615003, "title": "Django hooks are uncalled", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/331", "created_at": "2013-03-04T11:30:43Z", "comments": 0, "state": "open"}
