{"body": "If I have two steps where one is a substring of the other, eg:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n@step(\"I log in\")\r\ndef login_one(step):\r\n    pass\r\n\r\n@step(\"I log in on the checkout page\")\r\ndef login_two(step):\r\n    pass\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen if I create a test using the latter one, either of these functions might be run depending on the capricious order of the STEP_REGISTRY dict.\r\n\r\nIn core.py, line 305 in Step._get_match, when iterating STEP_REGISTRY.items, sort by string length longest first to avoid this bug.\r\n\r\nI'll try and submit a patch later if I can.", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/228/events", "updated_at": "2012-02-16T22:30:43Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/228/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/228/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/228", "number": 228, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/sixohsix", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/63fff8bad1b8bfffb6bc56aab93e4bef?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6003822a5989689befd308ce1be4ac75.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/received_events", "gravatar_id": "63fff8bad1b8bfffb6bc56aab93e4bef", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/sixohsix/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "sixohsix", "type": "User", "id": 40615, "followers_url": "https://ap