{"body": "Hi, Runner.run() method has a generic error handler (\"except:\") which tries to dump the traceback using traceback.print_exc(), but the traceback module is never imported and so the exception is completly ignored.\r\n\r\nHere is a patch to simplify the error handling. It replaces the generic \"except:\" by \"except Exception, err:\" to not catch SystemExit or KeyboardInterrupt anymore (at least on Python 2.5+).\r\n\r\n```\r\ndiff --git a/lettuce/__init__.py b/lettuce/__init__.py\r\nindex 3e1d473..f28911c 100644\r\n--- a/lettuce/__init__.py\r\n+++ b/lettuce/__init__.py\r\n@@ -128,41 +128,33 @@ class Runner(object):\r\n             self.output.print_no_features_found(self.loader.base_dir)\r\n             return\r\n \r\n-        failed = False\r\n         try:\r\n             for filename in features_files:\r\n                 feature = Feature.from_file(filename)\r\n                 results.append(\r\n                     feature.run(self.scenarios))\r\n-\r\n         except exceptions.LettuceSyntaxError, e:\r\n             sys.stderr.write(e.msg)\r\n-            failed = True\r\n-        except:\r\n-            e = sys.exc_info()[1]\r\n-            print \"Died with %s\" % str(e)\r\n-            traceback.print_exc()\r\n-            failed = True\r\n-\r\n-        finally:\r\n-            if failed:\r\n-                raise SystemExit(2)\r\n-\r\n-            total = TotalResult(results)\r\n-\r\n-            call_hook('after', 'all', total)\r\n-\r\n-            finished_at = datetime.now()\r\n-            time_took = finished_at - started_at\r\n-\r\n-            hours = time_took.seconds / 60 / 60\r\n-            minutes = time_took.seconds / 60\r\n-            seconds = time_took.seconds\r\n-            if hours:\r\n-                print  \"(finished within %d hours)\" % hours\r\n-            elif minutes:\r\n-                print  \"(finished within %d minutes)\" % minutes\r\n-            elif seconds:\r\n-                print  \"(finished within %d seconds)\" % seconds\r\n-\r\n-            return total\r\n+            raise SystemExit(2)\r\n+        except Exception, err:\r\n+            print \"Died with [%s] %s\" % (type(err), str(err))\r\n+            raise SystemExit(2)\r\n+\r\n+        total = TotalResult(results)\r\n+\r\n+        call_hook('after', 'all', total)\r\n+\r\n+        finished_at = datetime.now()\r\n+        time_took = finished_at - started_at\r\n+\r\n+        hours = time_took.seconds / 60 / 60\r\n+        minutes = time_took.seconds / 60\r\n+        seconds = time_took.seconds\r\n+        if hours:\r\n+            print  \"(finished within %d hours)\" % hours\r\n+        elif minutes:\r\n+            print  \"(finished within %d minutes)\" % minutes\r\n+        elif seconds:\r\n+            print  \"(finished within %d seconds)\" % seconds\r\n+\r\n+        return total\r\n```", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/221/events", "updated_at": "2013-01-28T23:55:23Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/221/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/221/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/221", "number": 221, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/haypo", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/daa45563a98419bb1b6b63904ce71f95?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fb26e29216472c09c3d0cdb53b33294dc.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/received_events", "gravatar_id": "daa45563a98419bb1b6b63904ce71f95", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "haypo", "type": "User", "id": 194129, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/haypo/followers"}, "milestone": null, "closed_at": "2013-01-28T23:55:23Z", "pull_request": {"diff_url": null, "html_url": null, "patch_url": null}, "id": 2870798, "title": "Fix handling SystemExit in Runner().run()", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/221", "created_at": "2012-01-17T16:20:58Z", "comments": 3, "state": "closed"}
