{"body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n```gherkin\r\nScenario: Background doesn't recognize Examples\r\n  Given I have a Background\r\n  And  I have a Scenario Outline\r\n  When I define a step in the Background\r\n  And the Background has a variable <variable>\r\n  And the <variable> is defined in the Scenario Examples table\r\n  Then the step doesn't match the variable with the Examples definition\r\n  And I have to duplicate code\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Deliverables\r\n\r\n```gherkin\r\nScenario: Background recognizes Examples\r\n  Given I have a Background\r\n  And  I have a Scenario Outline\r\n  When I define a step in the Background\r\n  And the Background has a variable <variable>\r\n  And the <variable> is defined in the Scenario Examples table\r\n  Then the step match's the variable with the Examples definition\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\n#### Prerequisites\r\n- [Get Example table as column for Step](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L354-L358) \r\n- [ Transform Examples table to json for Step](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/strings.py#L229-L260) \r\n- [ Set Scenario Examples table](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L564-L588) - the outlines are passed as arguments\r\n- [Compute Feature background lines](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L1158) & [Initialize Feature Background](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L1160-L1166)\r\n- [Parse feature line to compute background lines](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L1104-L1120) \r\n- [Scenario compiles Scenario and Examples](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L832)\r\n- [Background compiles only lines which start with Background](https://github.com/marianitadn/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L1108-L1109)\r\n\r\n#### TODO\r\n- [logical step in completing this story]\r\n\r\n#### Files\r\n- [path to a file involved in this story]\r\n\r\n#### Notes\r\n- [peculiar aspect relevant this story]\r\n\r\n#### #ETA [0-2]p", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/428/events", "updated_at": "2014-01-31T16:41:36Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/428/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/428/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/428", "number": 428, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/marianitadn", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/4ede901d02edfca3e35db27377f13d5d?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F4dc198724b8b7b3af7716efc890fead1.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/received_events", "gravatar_id": "4ede901d02edfca3e35db27377f13d5d", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "marianitadn", "type": "User", "id": 1681405, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/marianitadn/followers"}, "milestone": null, "closed_at": null, "pull_request": {"diff_url": null, "html_url": null, "patch_url": null}, "id": 26698049, "title": "Background should identify Scenario's Examples table", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/428", "created_at": "2014-01-31T16:41:16Z", "comments": 0, "state": "open"}
