{"body": "Right now, the second step in the following set:\r\n\r\n    When I do X\r\n    And I do Y\r\n\r\nwill include the \"And\" part in the matching string, which means it won't match if you tried to write:\r\n\r\n    When I do Y\r\n\r\nIn another scenario.\r\n\r\nI think all \"And\" steps should replace \"and\" with the correct word from the step they follow. So if you have:\r\n\r\n    When X\r\n    And Y\r\n    And Z\r\n\r\nthis will match against steps using the text \"When X\", \"When Y\" and \"When Z\".\r\n\r\nI'd also suggest adding specific given/when/then specific, so you can write:\r\n\r\n@when(\"I do Y\")\r\ndef when_i_do_y(step): pass", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/100/events", "updated_at": "2011-07-05T11:50:08Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/100/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/100/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/100", "number": 100, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/gfxmonk", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/80523678d9f1e048244f6f17f2c53427?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F9f3d342d38e036a9137ef3e270d9d79c.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/received_events", "gravatar_id": "80523678d9f1e048244f6f17f2c53427", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gfxmonk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "gfx