{"body": "\r\nThe @step decorator adds items into the STEP_REGISTRY by using the compiled regex address.\r\n\r\nWhen you have steps which overlap substantially, you may find that lettuce will pick the wrong regex as a match (it stops at the first match, when it should stop at the first **longest prefix** match).\r\n\r\nExample text which caused this problem was:\r\n\r\n    @step('a visible suggestion with the title \"(.*)\"')\r\n    def function_one(step, title):\r\n        pass\r\n\r\n    @step('a visible suggestion with the title \"(.*)\" in category \"(.*)\"')\r\n    def function_two(step, title, category):\r\n        pass\r\n\r\nYou can work around this by changing the longer text but chasing down this bug is (was!) time consuming.", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/171/events", "updated_at": "2011-09-17T13:22:26Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/171/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/171/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/171", "number": 171, "assignee": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/3fa0df5c54f5ac0f8652d992d7d24039?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F0614053c29836afdd915d777401128a9.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3fa0df5c54f5ac0f865