{"body": "I've implemented steps-from-step-definitions for feature parity with [Cucumber](http://github.com/aslakhellesoy/cucumber/wiki/Calling-Steps-from-Step-Definitions). The changes allow the following step definitions:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n@step('I am huge')\r\ndef hugeness(step):\r\n    step.given('I have gone to the gym')     # or .then() or .when()\r\n    world.huge_people.append(\"Me\")\r\n\r\n@step('I have all the ladies')\r\ndef ladies(step):\r\n    step.behave_as(\"\"\"\r\n        Given I am huge\r\n        And I am brainy\r\n        And I actually talk to girls\r\n    \"\"\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nDocumentation is included for this, in the tutorial section.", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/75/events", "updated_at": "2011-12-21T19:27:28Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/75/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/75/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/pull/75", "number": 75, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/ajtack", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/5de821af118f9733cab404a0def29387?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd244da6f35a9195bf35fc957adf9b9d1.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5de821af118f9733cab404a0def29387", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "ajtack",