{"body": "Hi Gabriel et al,\r\n\r\nThis change brings the output of Lettuce more in line with that of Cucumber. Instead of\r\n\r\n    ...\r\n    Scenario: Something\r\n        Given I have no space\r\n    Scenario: Something Else\r\n        Then I am unhappy\r\n\r\nThis update puts a blank line between a scenario and any previous steps. I find this helpful when reading output.\r\n\r\n    ...\r\n    Scenario: Something\r\n        Given I have space\r\n\r\n    Scenario: Something Else\r\n        Then I am quite content\r\n\r\n--\r\nAndres", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/74/events", "updated_at": "2010-10-13T22:12:32Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/74/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/74/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/pull/74", "number": 74, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/ajtack", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/5de821af118f9733cab404a0def29387?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd244da6f35a9195bf35fc957adf9b9d1.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5de821af118f9733cab404a0def29387", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "ajtack", "type": "User", "id": 48368, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ajtack/followers"}, "milestone": null, "closed_at"