{"body": "Lettuce is incorrectly running the background **before** running the before hooks on each scenario in contradiction to the requirements of the Gherkin syntax that expects it be run before each scenario but **after** the hooks. (See https://github.com/cucumber/cucumber/wiki/Background)\r\n\r\nBecause I do all my database flushing in a `@before.each_scenario`, this error prevents me from combining my common setup code for a feature in a single background section since my database is reset after the background section is completed and before the scenario is run.\r\n\r\n`Scenario.run()` needs to be passed an optional background and the inner function `run_scenario` should call `Background.run()` before `Step.run_all`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/blob/master/lettuce/core.py#L697\r\n\r\nLet me know if you want me to submit a pull-request.\r\n", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/326/events", "updated_at": "2013-03-03T09:13:31Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/326/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/326/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/326", "number": 326, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/kevinastone", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinastone/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/f24ff8f4aaea78959060fd4e0553c697?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fb9c3fd65b54bbadf36cbacc38970354c.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kevinaston