{"body": "When testing a large project with long, slow tests, it's useful to fail fast -- stop execution if a single test fails.\r\n\r\nThis adds a \"--fail-fast\" option to the command line and django runners.  If any scenario in any feature fails, test execution stops.  Default is False, so doesn't change behavior unless you want it.", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/224/events", "updated_at": "2013-01-29T08:24:02Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/224/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/224/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/pull/224", "number": 224, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/yourcelf", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/780278dd7b2d6bb187413a3cfcfb48cf?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fef926983fef6f9c7f1207289ac8a0331.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/received_events", "gravatar_id": "780278dd7b2d6bb187413a3cfcfb48cf", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "yourcelf", "type": "User", "id": 21318, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yourcelf/followers"}, "milestone": null, "closed_at": "2013-01-24T23:13:12Z", "pull_request": {"diff_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/pull/224.diff", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/pull/224"