{"body": "Currently if lettuce cannot find a step it generates a default code for it.\r\nYou can use this code to add a command that generates the steps:\r\n        \r\n```python\r\n        wrt(\"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\\n\")\r\n        wrt(\"from lettuce import step\\n\\n\")\r\n\r\n        last = len(total.proposed_definitions) - 1\r\n        for current, step in enumerate(total.proposed_definitions):\r\n            method_name = step.proposed_method_name\r\n            wrt(\"@step(u'%s')\\n\" % step.proposed_sentence)\r\n            wrt(\"def %s:\\n\" % method_name)\r\n            wrt(\"    assert False, 'This step must be implemented'\")\r\n            if current is last:\r\n                wrt(\"\\033[0m\")\r\n\r\n            wrt(\"\\n\")\r\n```", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/217/events", "updated_at": "2012-02-16T19:08:51Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/217/labels{/name}", "labels": [], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/217/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/217", "number": 217, "assignee": null, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/thedrow", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/5bf5f3464f90521d91dc889b71d2955a?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6c1b3d4b67b87271c3dec4ab370b0a14.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedrow/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5bf5f3464f90521d91dc889b71d2955a", "starred_u