{"body": "I've just spent 2 hours debugging why I can't access django.core.mail.outbox. \r\nThis led me to discovery of ThreadedServer which is not threaded at all, rather it's sub-process.\r\nBecause sub-process has separate memory, outbox on the parent process stays empty forever.\r\nI'm not sure what's the best way to fix this, but some documentation should help.\r\n\r\nSince [this](http://cilliano.com/blog/2011/02/07/django-bdd-with-lettuce-and-splinter/) is one of Google's top post on using lettuce with Django, I think there should be some more clarification .", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/215/events", "updated_at": "2013-01-28T23:55:55Z", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/215/labels{/name}", "labels": [{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/labels/high-priority", "color": "e10c02", "name": "high-priority"}], "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/215/comments", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao/lettuce/issues/215", "number": 215, "assignee": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/gabrielfalcao", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://gravatar.com/avatar/3fa0df5c54f5ac0f8652d992d7d24039?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F0614053c29836afdd915d777401128a9.png&r=x", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gabrielfalcao/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3fa0df5c54f5ac0f8652d992d7d24039", "starred_url": "https://api.gith